    <p>We re­fer to Mr An­drew Har­ris’ let­ter (On­line bank­ing: Let down by old-fash­ioned service de­liv­ery, Dec 16).</p>
    <p>We have been in touch with Mr Har­ris and ap­pre­ci­ate the op­por­tu­nity to clar­ify, and will look into im­prove­ments to the ac­count open­ing process with­out putting our cus­tomers’ pri­vacy and se­cu­rity at risk.</p>
    <p>Mervyn Koh</p>
    <p>Man­ag­ing Di­rec­tor and Coun­try Head Busi­ness Bank­ing</p>
